[PKDR] Package Keeper Directory Runtime

Usage:
  pkdr <command> [options]

Commands:
  add <env> <package>      Add a package to an environment
  remove <env> <package>   Remove a package from an environment
  enter <env>              Enter an isolated environment
  init <env>               Initialize an environment
  init -a                  Initialize all environments
  list                     List available environments
  show <env>               Show packages in an environment
  update                   Update PKDR
  uninstall                Remove PKDR
  export -a /path/to/      To export all environments
  export <env> /path/to    To export a specific environment
  import /path/to          To import your environment
  -v, --version            Show version
  --help                   Show this help page

Description:
  PKDR is a lightweight, open-source utility for Termux that
  preserves and reconstructs development environments.

  Save your setup once. Rebuild it anywhere.

Developed by Nishit Samar (AlloyDark) — 2026

